Dialogs.Dialog: Hehe. Did you want to talk to Rinko？
Hello, it's me. Is it okay now？
I'm glad you called. What's up？
Hello, it's me. Can I talk to you now？
It's me. Is it okay now？
It's me, can we talk now？
Today, when we head home, can we pass by ▲デート場所▲？
Do you want to go to ▲デート場所▲？
Okay, I'm looking forward to it.
Hmm～, I don't think I can make it...
Not today... invite me another day.
Well, I'll see you next time.
Why don't you skip class and we'll go there now？ Hehe.
No, we can't. Besides, it's better to save the fun for later.
Rinko likes to stop by after school.
Last time you stood me up on an appointment. How can I get you to apologize？
Sorry. Don't worry this time！ I'll make sure you have fun.
I'll make sure you make up for the time you stood me up before.
Don't stand me up again, okay？ Rinko is looking forward to it.
Sorry. Next time, I'll make it a fun date for sure, as an apology.
I'll forgive you for leaving Rinko alone the other day... I can't help it.
Sorry. I didn't mean to do that on purpose...
I'll make it up to you for leaving Rinko alone before.
Now I forgive you for leaving Rinko alone the other day. I guess it's inevitable.
Thank you. I'm sorry about that.
Since you haven't seen me at all lately... I was pretty worried about you.
We haven't seen each other at all recently. If I hadn't seen you any more, I would have forgotten about you！
Sorry, sorry. Don't forget about me, okay？
Thank goodness. Rinko was wondering if she did something... since you didn't see me at all.
Hey, I have a ▲生成選択肢１▲. Why don't we go on ▲月▲▲日▲ to ▲デート場所▲？
It's a little late for that.
Yay. I wanted to go to there.
Sounds nice. Rinko is interested in that.
Did you by any chance know that Rinko wanted to go？ Hehe.
Heh, I didn't know there was such a thing. Well, it's okay.
Okay, fine. I'm curious to see what it's like.
Yeah, it's okay. I wonder how it feels.
Hmmm, I don't think I can go. Too bad.
I'm not in the mood... better not.
Sorry... Invite me again if anything else happens.
I can't do it that day, so can't we do it another day？
What shall I do？ I'm starting to have some fun now.
Haha, you're getting ahead of yourself.
Well, let's just call it settled, shall we？
I probably won't care about that day's class. It's your fault.
Mine？ Well, I'm glad you're looking forward to it.
You mean after school. That would be a good idea.
Well, I'll be looking forward to it. I'll do some research.
It could be quite a long wait. As if it will live up to expectations.
Thanks for adding to Rinko's enjoyment.
No problem. I'll see you later.
Hello？ It's Rinko. Can we talk now？
Hey, you know, on our way home today... do you want to go somewhere with me？
Let's stop by somewhere on the way home today.
Um, do you want to stop by somewhere with me on our way home？
See you later. I'll be waiting for you at the school gate.
Then I'll meet you at the school gate after school.
Okay, I'll see you after school.
Yay！ I'll be waiting for you at the school gate after school. Hehe.
...sorry. Let's not do it this time.
Hmm, okay. I'll see you next time.
Sorry！ I knew I had to cancel this time.
Okay. We'll settle on that day.
I'm just not sure I can make it that day...
We just met, right？ Well... Rinko isn't complaining.
You want to see Rinko so bad？ Hehe... it's okay.
You want to see me again？ I don't mind.
We just met, remember？ I can't help it.
We just met a while ago. But okay.
Then how about going to ▲デート場所▲？
I hadn't seen you in a while, so I was a little nervous. Thanks for asking me out. See you later.
Okay, then let's meet at ▲デート場所▲.
It's been a while since you've asked me to meet up with you, hasn't it？ I'll hurry up and meet you there.... hehe.
Okay, I'll see you at the ▲デート場所▲
Ok. I'm glad it's been so long since we've done something like this. I can't wait to see you, so I'll be there as soon as I can.
Sorry... But I just had to see you.
You know, I said I don't want to see you.
...but I really wanted to see you.
Sorry. I know, but I really need to see you.
...I can't guarantee that I'll be there. See you then.
I didn't say I'd go. See you.
Still, I'll be waiting. See you.
Hello... it's Rinko. I'd like to see you now...
Ah, it's Rinko. I need to see you right now... tell me it's okay.
Um, this is Rinko. Hey... I was wondering if I could meet you right now... Can't we？
So, is okay to meet at ▲デート場所▲？
I'll be waiting. You'll come soon, okay？ Absolutely, okay？
Then let's meet at ▲デート場所▲.
That's okay. Hurry up and get here, okay？ I'll be really angry if you're late.
Well, let's meet at ▲デート場所▲.
Yay. I'm sorry for being so selfish, okay？ ...hehe.
I want to see you too, so that's fine.
Okay, I'll see you at the ▲時▲ in ▲デート場所▲.
Okay, I'll wait for you... I'd really like to see you right now.
Sorry. I'll go so as not to keep you waiting. See you later.
Okay. Then at ▲時▲ in ▲デート場所▲.
You'd better come. If you are even a little late, I'll kick you.
Okay, it's decided. Then at ▲時▲ in ▲デート場所▲.
Yes, I'm happy. Thank you for listening to Rinko's selfishness.
I don't think you're being selfish. I'll see you later.
I told you I really want to see you！
It's a little too much for me... sorry.
I don't want that！ Rinko wants to see you... is it absolutely impossible？
Really, I can't make it... Sorry.
I see... I can't help it, it's sudden. It's fine... don't worry about it.
I'm really sorry... You took the time to invite me.
Hmm, I just can't do it...
Oh, I see. Rinko can't ask for this much？ ...I don't mind. Idiot！
Really, I'm sorry. Let's do it another time.
Sorry... I can't do it no matter how hard I try.
I see... I understand. I'm sorry for being so selfish, okay？ Rinko... will put up with it this time.
Really, I'm sorry, okay？ Thanks for inviting me. I'll see you next time.
Hey... I just thought I'd say thanks.
You know, because you asked me out on a date.
That's why we're in a relationship, and that's what we're supposed to do, right？
But it's not exactly a normal date. That's why...
I see. If you're pleased, I'm happy too.
Well, I just thought I'd say thank you. Just in case.
You asked me out on a date.
But it felt different and special, you know？ I was happy.
I'm glad to hear you say so.
You asked me out on a date, didn't you？ So, you know, thanks.
It's normal for boyfriends to invite girlfriends.
But Rinko thought this date was special, not ordinary. I'm happy.
Thank you. I'm happy too, so I'll say thank you.
Hey, how many hours until the date？
Well, I don't think that matters.
Because... even if you know how many hours it is, it doesn't make the throbbing go away.
If I were to talk about this stuff, my expectations would be raised.
(This must be entertaining at all costs.)
I'm looking forward to our next date.
Yeah. But for Rinko, anywhere with you is special.
...you're unusually honest, you must be embarrassed.
Hey？ Did you get that Rinko can't wait for the date？
If you say it that clearly, I think it will be understood.
Really？ So you know I'm looking forward to it？
Is there a difference between waiting and looking forward to something？
I have to be in good condition by the time of the date.
I'm not exaggerating. You should be prepared for anything.
What do you want me to do？
To avoid catching a cold, gargle and wash your hands when you get home, eat nutritious food, and go to bed early...
(The point is, take care of yourself, huh...)
Then I would agree with you.
This eagerness to wait makes the date of the day exciting again.
I heard it's supposed to be cloudy on the day of the date.
Well, that's it. It might be a nice way to spend some time.
Hmm, that's not so bad. Well, that's good.
I looked at the weather forecast and it was supposed to rain on our date.
I don't like it when it rains because it makes me feel like I'm going to be depressed.
On the day of the event, I wonder if the rain clouds will go away because of my power？ Haha！
...are you serious？ It'll be cold then.
Have you prepared for tomorrow yet？
Not yet. What about you, ▲小早川＊▲？
No, not yet. What should I prepare？
Maybe clothes to wear tomorrow, or things to take with you.
You can bring it them... but it's like a field trip. Haha.
What time do you plan to get up tomorrow？
I don't know, I haven't decided yet.
Well then, Rinko will decide for you. You must get up at 5:30 in the morning！
...it's too early. Besides, the date is in the evening, remember？
No！ It's all about spirit in these things.
Hey, it's really tomorrow, right？ Our date.
I've been wanting it to come quickly... so I could not believe that it would finally be tomorrow.
So what do you expect for tomorrow？
Haha. Don't worry, I'm sure it's tomorrow. Be sure to come.
Of course I know. It's our date.
If you are late tomorrow, I will be angry, okay？ It's outrageous to be late.
I'll be fine. Don't threaten me before we start.
I'm looking forward to our date tomorrow. Hehe.
You remember our date today, don't you？
I'll enjoy myself to the fullest today.
I've been excited all morning today. And you？
Maybe I should arrange the next date, an earlier date.
Yes. I can't wait for it, too.
I can't wait for the date, it's so stressful waiting for it.
(I hope you don't direct that stress at me.)
I was thinking about our next date and I wanted to hear your voice.
I see. Well, then, as much as you want.
Sorry！ I'll be there soon, just wait for me.
I'll give you five more minutes.
Hello, this is Rinko. Do you know what I want to say？
Really？ I was worried about you. I'll be waiting for you, so please come soon.
Yeah, I'm so sorry. I'll be right there！
Sorry... I don't even have an excuse.
So what are you going to do？
I'll make it up to you next time
Hey, what do you think you're doing？ Do you think you can keep Rinko waiting this long and get away with it for free？
Well, what do you want to do now？
I'll make this up to you later
Hey... Rinko has been waiting for you for a long time, okay？
What do we do now？ Should I wait？ or, next time？
Let me make it up to you next time
Do you mind if we start now？
Okay... Then, Rinko will be at the meeting place again.
Thank you. I'll definitely be there this time.
Would you still be willing to go on a date with me now？
I can't help it... Then get your ass to the rendezvous point！ Understood？
I'm on my way. Is that okay？
Okay. I'll be waiting for you at the rendezvous.
I'm really sorry. I'll be right there.
I'll make it up to you next time, I promise...
I'll make this up to you next time, I promise. Sorry about today！
Oh, I see... I get it. Don't forget that word, right？
...can I make it up to you sometime
I get it. A shame, but I'll see you next time... I'll be looking forward to it.
Why didn't you come today？ Did you forget our appointment？
"I'm sorry" comes first, not excuses. Come on, say it.
Hah... I'll let you off the hook this time.
Thanks. I'll be careful next time.
I can't hear you. Did you say, "I'm sorry"？
I can't believe you stood me up on a date.
Sorry... I didn't do it on purpose.
Ah, I see. Anyway, you've got me worried.
Hey... did Rinko do something wrong？
Because lately, you've been acting kind in a certain way... It makes me feel uneasy.
I see... I'll try to get in touch with you more.
If you do that, I might be less worried...
I see... So, shall we meet now？
Yeah. I'll be waiting for you at ▲デート場所▲.
You care too much about that stuff. It's all in your mind.
I'll be a little more careful.
How are you doing？ You're looking pretty bad, huh？
Don't worry. I'll be fine after a little rest.
You have to sleep well, you know. Rinko will make sure to visit you, too.
Hey... are you okay？ I was a little worried, so I called.
Ah, I think I'm going to be okay somehow.
Don't be too hard on yourself, take a good rest.
Thank you. I feel a little better.
Let's go on another date. Okay？
Of course. I might ask you out even if you say you don't want to.
How was our date？ Tell me what you thought.
First of all, let me know what you think, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko thinks it wasn't bad... Not amazing, but it wasn't bad.
You mean it was good. So do I.
That was a fun date. I want to go again.
Rinko, you know, feels so happy right now.
Me too. Thanks to you, ▲小早川＊▲.
That's mutual. Anyway, it was a great date.
Yeah. We really had a good time, didn't we？
I've been so nervous ever since we left.
Me too. Our date was great.
It really was the happiest I've ever felt. Thanks.
Let's make it a better date next time.
Guess how Rinko is feeling right now.
Close！ The correct answer was that I'm so happy. Great date, thanks.
I see. I appreciate it, too.
I appreciate all you did for me for our date.
You're welcome. I'm glad you enjoyed it.
If this were every day, it would be amazing.
Haha. These things are fine, because it's just once in a while.
I know. That's how much fun I had！
You know, I just wanted to thank you.
That's right. Because the date was extra fun.
Then, I should also thank you ▲小早川＊▲.
You can't！ Rinko says it first. Thanks for the special time... hehe.
This date must have been a lot of work and preparation, right？
For the sake of my cute girlfriend, I mean this is no big deal.
Hehe... I'm so happy. It gave me a special memory. Thanks.
Yeah. Let's go back and make some special memories.
You know, I think I might quite like the idea of a date at your house.
Well, then, you'd better clean up every day so that I can go there whenever I want.
Your room is kind of relaxing.
Yeah？ Then you can stay forever. Just kidding！
I had a great time at your house. Hey, can I come back again？
Of course. Come as much as you want！
...I'm not sure if you can put it that way.
Let's hear what you think of coming to my house, shall we？
I feel totally at home. Thank you.
Good. Well, come visit me again.
We are in Rinko's room right now, but I feel like it has some of your vibe left in it.
I don't know if it's a sign or what... anyway, I feel good！
Did you have fun at Rinko's house？
Yeah, it was fun. Can I go again？
Of course. Anytime！ ...Not necessarily, but you're welcome.
You know, thanks for lending me your bath.
I think I might have been a little bit nervous.
The food on our date was delicious.
Yes, I'll keep that in mind.
Rinko likes the taste of the restaurant we ate at on our date.
Heh, so you really liked it.
Maybe a date meal is pretty important.
Yes, I'll keep that in mind.
I think I'm looking at you in a new light.
The restaurant where we dined on our date, because it was the right choice for Rinko's tastes.
I see. I guess I was right.
Hey, what are you doing now？
I guess I was in a daze for now.
How do you do that anyway？
That's a little weird, if you ask me.
It's not that I have any business with you, but I was wondering what you were doing.
I knew you would say that...
Hey, what were you doing just now？
Hey, I suddenly wanted to hear your voice.
I see, I also wanted to hear your voice ▲小早川＊▲.
A heart to heart, huh. Hmm.
Do you have any interesting stories？
That's abrupt... I can't think of anything if you ask me suddenly.
Well, that's fine. I just wanted to hear your voice.
I see. But I think I'll prepare something next time.
What's wrong？ Did I say something weird？
No. I'm just happy to hear your voice.
I see, then me too, ▲小早川＊▲.
Sorry it's so late. Are you still awake？
I called you because I couldn't sleep. I thought I could sleep when I heard your voice.
Is my voice a substitute for a lullaby？ Haha.
I don't know, I couldn't sleep, so I called... Is it okay if I talk to you？
Sure, as much as you want.
Thanks. Your voice is so soothing. I wonder why？
Don't you think we are on the same wavelength？
I'll stay up a little longer. What about you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko can't sleep... I tried to go to sleep and when I closed my eyes, I saw your face, so I called you.
Before I go to bed, I thought I'd say good night.
That's why you took the trouble to call me, thank you.
Before going to bed, you say good night, right？
Good night. Make sure you dream about Rinko.
Haha, that's a lot of pressure. Good night.
You know, I just wanted to say good night.
Ah！ Rinko was going to say it first. Um, good night. Have a nice dream... hehe.
Rinko might have be on duty tomorrow as a committee member. It's a hassle.
I'm feeling dull and sleepy thinking about work... Good night.
Yeah, good night. Good luck tomorrow.
Oh, I'm so tired. I think I'll sleep well today.
There are a lot of things going on. Rinko is very busy. Well, good night.
Oh, good night. I'll go to bed too.
Good job to you too, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko is not that tired, she is young. But I'm going to bed early. Good night.
I'm just one year older. Well, that's okay. Good night.
Don't worry, I woke up perfectly when I heard your voice.
You sound sleepy. I told you to be sharp.
Hmm... okay！ I'll get up in spirit.
What do you think of Rinko's wake-up call？ Are you happy？
Nice. I think it's going to be a good day.
It's morning already, so why don't you get up？
Where. Your voice is totally asleep, you know？ Don't hang up the phone and then go back to sleep.
Okay, get up. Early bird gets the better of the three. Yes, how much is 3 sentences now？
Hmm... don't give me problems in the morning.
Rinko will let you know when the morning arrives.
You've got to get up. You don't oversleep after getting Rinko's wake-up call, you know.
You're right. Thanks for waking me up.
Haven't you been slacking off on your committee work lately？ You should get on the job.
I see... when I was on duty？
Hah... I knew it. Just come on, Rinko will be there too.
Okay, I get it. I'll be careful.
I gotta go then, okay？ Bye-bye.
It's getting late, I should probably go.
I'd love to talk some more... but it's pretty late. See you later. Bye-bye.
I'd love to talk more, but I have to hang up now. Let's talk about the rest of this when we see each other again, okay？ Bye-bye.
What？ Rinko is pretty angry right now.
If it's my fault, of course I have to, right？ Sorry.
...Rinko looks like an idiot for being angry all by herself.
...I can't help. Instead, the next time I see you, I'll just... Anyway, I forgive you.
(Looks like you're in a better mood...)
I think the situation is mutual.
Then let's get on with it.
What's with that... acting like an adult.
Shut up, old man... No, I get it, we'll make up.
(Looks like you're in a better mood...)
I thought about it, but it wasn't my bad, right？
So you're saying Rinko is wrong？
I wouldn't say so... but can't only blame me.
...well, maybe Rinko was a bit selfish.
It's no use fighting like this, let's make up. Right？
(Looks like you're in a better mood...)
...incoming call. Looks like you left a message, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hello, it's Rinko. It's your birthday today, right？
Congratulations, in a manner of speaking. I really wanted to say it in person.
(You remembered me and I'm sorry I couldn't get it...)
It's Rinko. Today is an important anniversary for both of us, right？
That's why I called... well, it can't be helped.
(I see, that's why you called me...)
Happy New Year！ It's me, Rinko.
I'll leave it for now, since it doesn't look like you're going to answer it. See you.
(You went out of your way to call me. I would have liked to hear it in person if I could.)
Hello, it's Rinko... I was wondering if we could meet... I'll be in touch.
(Oh no... I was so excited to be invited.)
Hi, it's Rinko. I called because I wanted to see you, but why is your phone going straight to voicemail？
(...should I invite her over here later？)
Um, hey, I wanted to see you... But if you're busy, we can do it another time. Bye.
...it's Rinko. I wanted to talk to you about a date... Well, nevermind.
I was going to ask you out on a date, but you didn't answer...
It's Rinko. I was calling to see if we could go on a date sometime... Maybe some other time.
(I'm sorry you had to call me.)
Hello, it's Rinko. Well... it's not really anything, but I was just wondering. See you later.
(What's going on？ I'll call you later.)
